elements.name: As a user, I want to open new application for Well Permit

steps.name: User launch the Access my water homepage
User should login with valid username and password
User click on Start New Application
User click on Water Affecting Activity Permits
User click on Well Construction Permit Application
User click on Add new button
User fill the contact information page
